<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":4} -->
<h4>#3) Project-based AR</h4>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This kind uses synthetic light projected on the physical surfaces to detect the interaction of the user with the surfaces. It is used on holograms like in Star Wars and other sci-fi movies.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>The below image is an example showing a sword projection in AR project-based AR headset:</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":132236,"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
